flowchart TD
    Client[Browser Client: HTML5 / Bootstrap 5 / Vanilla JS]
    
    subgraph Flask Application Controller
        Routes[Routing, Session & API Controllers]
        Auth[Session Auth Manager]
        Heuristics[Heuristic Feature Extractor]
        ML[scikit-learn Random Forest Model]
        PDF[ReportLab PDF Engine]
    end
    
    subgraph Persistence Layer
        DB[(MySQL / SQLite Database)]
    end
    
    Client <-->|HTTP Post / Ajax JSON| Routes
    Routes <--> Auth
    Routes --> Heuristics
    Heuristics -->|Feature List| ML
    ML -->|Threat Verification Verdict| Routes
    Routes --> PDF
    Routes <-->|SQLAlchemy ORM| DB
